  "preflight": [
    {
      "op": "log",
      "note": "No persisted-preference staging is required. The start page (crm-vehicles.html) loads with the left rail collapsed and the CRM secondary sidebar expanded by design (probe-verified July 11 on CDP 9224); the KPI band (.a-metrics / .a-metric) and Vehicle Status card render above the fold with stable rects. Every page reached by a rail click self-expands its own secondary sidebar on load (crm-customers, settings, support-tickets all verified). The two Settings submenus this lesson needs (Users & Security -> Blacklisted, Operations -> Cancellation Reasons) load COLLAPSED on settings.html, so the timeline expands each with an unless-guarded menu-header click (usExpand/opsExpand) that only ever OPENS the group before clicking the in-app link. All targets/predicates were live-probed against the running tenant; the demo member opened for steps 2-3 is CUST-4420000001643501 (VISA CARDHOLDER, Cleanest Ultra Unlimited, Active, plate 141510974212 linked) — a neutral generic-named account carrying real live diagnostic values (BARCODE 141510974212, STATUS Active, NEXT CHARGE Feb 10 2026, all four header chips)."
    }
  ],
